-- China’s Yi Wins First Gold Medal of London Olympics in Shooting
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2012-07-28T10:25:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-28/china-s-yi-wins-first-gold-medal-of-london-olympics-in-shooting.html
China ’s Yi Siling won the first gold
medal at the London Olympics, taking the women’s 10-meter air
rifle competition.  Poland’s Sylwia Bogacka won the silver medal and China’s Yu
Dan won the bronze medal.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
